      • setAttackTargetPriority

        public Agent setAttackTargetPriority(Agent.TargetingPriority attackTargetPriority)
        Change the priority of this agent when other agents try to find a new target. For best performance keep most agents on Agent.TargetingPriority.HIGHEST.

        Interceptors are assigned a low priority by default, the rest defaults to Agent.TargetingPriority.HIGHEST.
